%html
  %head
    %meta{:content => "text/html; charset=UTF-8", "http-equiv" => "Content-Type"}/
    %link{:href => "style.css", :rel => "stylesheet"}/
    %title FURIMA
  %body
    %header.header
      .header__inner
        .header__inner__main
          .header__inner__main__icon
            %a{:href => "/"}
              %img{:src => "assets/logo/logo.png"}/
          .header__inner__search
            %form{"accept-charset" => "UTF-8", :action => "#", :method => "get"}
              %input{:name => "utf8", :type => "hidden"}/
              %input.header__inner__search__input{:name => "key", :placeholder => "キーワードから探す"}/
            %form.header__inner__search__button{:action => "/", :method => "post", :type => "submit"}
              %button{:type => "submit"}
                .header__inner__search__button__icon
                  %img{:src => "assets/icon/icon-search 1.png", class: "search" }/
        .nav
          %ul.nav__left
            %li.nav__left__category
              %a#catbtn{:href => "#"} カテゴリー
              .nav__left__category__tree
                %ul.categoryTree
            %li.nav__left__brand
              %a#brandbtn{:href => "#"} ブランド
              %ul.nav__left__brand__list
          %ul.nav__right
            %li.nav__right__login
              %a{:href => "#"} ログイン
            %li.nav__right__login__new
              %a{:href => "#"} 新規会員登録
    ​
    .main
      %section.main__visual
        .main__visual__content
          %h2.main__visual__content__subtitle
            %br/
            人生を変えるフリマアプリ
          %p.main__visual__content__text
            FURIMAはだれでもかんたんに出品・購入できる
            %br/
            フリマアプリです
          %a{:href => "アプリのリンク"}
            %img{:alt => "AppStoreからダウンロード", :height => "40", :src => "https://developer.apple.com/app-store/marketing/guidelines/images/badge-download-on-the-app-store.svg", class: "appstore1", :style => "margin: 10px 10px;"}/
          %a{:href => "アプリのリンク"}
            %img{:alt => "AppStoreからダウンロード", :height => "40", :src => "https://play.google.com/intl/ja/badges/static/images/badges/ja_badge_web_generic.png", class: "google1" }/
        .picture
      %section.main__introduction
        %h2.main__introduction__subtitle
          FURIMAが選ばれる3つの理由
        %ul.main__introduction__lists
          %li.main__introduction__lists__list
            .main__introduction__lists__list__pict
              %span.number 1
              %img{:src => "assets/pict/pict-reason-01.jpg"}/
            %h3.main__introduction__lists__list__text
              %span 3分
              ですぐに出品
            %p.main__introduction__lists__list__description
              スマホで入力するだけで簡単に出品できる！
          %li.main__introduction__lists__list
            .main__introduction__lists__list__pict
              %span.number 2
              %img{:src => "assets/pict/pict-reason-02.jpg"}/
            %h3.main__introduction__lists__list__text
              %span シンプル
              で使いやすい
            %p.main__introduction__lists__list__description
              めんどくさい入力は必要なく、検索も購入もスムーズ！
          / <li class="list list--last">
          %li.main__introduction__lists__list
            .main__introduction__lists__list__pict
              %span.number 3
              %img{:src => "assets/pict/pict-reason-03.jpg"}/
            %h3.main__introduction__lists__list__text
              手数料
              %span 業界最安
            %p.main__introduction__lists__list__description
              最大3%でお得に出品&amp;購入！
      %section.main__middle
        .main__middle__inner
          %h2.main__middle__inner__subtitle 会員数日本一位
          %p.main__middle__inner__text
            FURIMAは、フリマアプリで最も人気。
            %br/
            出品・購入回数も業界最多です！
            %br/
            ほしかったあの商品に出会えるかもしれません。
          %a{:href => "アプリのリンク"}
            %img{:alt => "AppStoreからダウンロード", :height => "40", :src => "https://developer.apple.com/app-store/marketing/guidelines/images/badge-download-on-the-app-store.svg", class: "appstore2", :style => "margin: 10px 10px;"}/
          %a{:href => "アプリのリンク"}
            %img{:alt => "AppStoreからダウンロード", :height => "40", :src => "https://play.google.com/intl/ja/badges/static/images/badges/ja_badge_web_generic.png", class: "google2" }/
      %section.main__features
        %h2.main__feautures__head FURIMAの特徴
        .main__feautures__head__items
          %section.main__feautures__head__items__item
            %figure.main__feautures__head__items__item__img
            %img{:src => "assets/icon/icon-01.png"}/
            %h3.main__feautures__head__items__item__topic 簡単に売り買いできる
            %p.main__feautures__head__items__item__detail
              スマホひとつで、いつでもどこでも簡単に出品・購入が可能！
          %section.main__feautures__head__items__item
            %figure.main__feautures__head__items__item__img
            %img{:src => "assets/icon/icon-03.png"}/
            %h3.main__feautures__head__items__item__topic 売上金は即日振込みに対応
            %p.main__feautures__head__items__item__detail
              午前9時までに振込を依頼いただければ、翌日に指定の口座に入金いたします!
          %section.main__feautures__head__items__item
            %figure.main__feautures__head__items__item__img
            %img{:src => "assets/icon/icon-04.png"}/
            %h3.main__feautures__head__items__item__topic 様々な支払いに対応
            %p.main__feautures__head__items__item__detail
              お支払いは、クレジットカードだけでなく、ポイントや売上金など多彩な方法があります。
